		"description": "<p><em>Wondrous item, (requires attunement)</em></p><p>When you make an Intelligence (Arcana) check to control a Sphere of Annihilation while you are holding this talisman, you double your proficiency bonus on the check. In addition, when you start your turn with control over a Sphere of Annihilation, you can use an action to levitate it 10 feet plus a number of additional feet equal to 10 × your Intelligence modifier.</p>",
